DESIGN ATTRIBUTION AND PROVENANCE

This design system is derived from and aligned with the Lighthouse HLTH marketing
site created in Framer (lighthousehlth.com). The visual design, component patterns,
brand identity, and design tokens are based on the original Framer project.

Original Design:
  Platform: Framer
  Brand: Lighthouse HLTH
  Owner: Indigo Labs LLC
  Designer: [As credited in Framer project]

This component library represents a technical implementation of the Lighthouse HLTH
visual identity for use in React/Next.js applications, ensuring brand consistency
across web, mobile, and application interfaces.

Design Extraction & Implementation:
  Method: Framer design token extraction and React component development
  Alignment: Pixel-perfect match to Framer marketing components
  Maintained by: Indigo Labs LLC engineering team

